HI Jim.  I am sorry for your loss.  Our pets are the only family that really
does give unconditional love.  But I wanted to drop a note to tell you I
heard the &#39;roar/meow&#39; around the 8 sec mark and I heard it!  It very well
could be a cat&#39;s meow.  Keep trying!

k


